They Two Ships land about Forty feet from the Crumbling Ark. Herald Defection 
Data Tranquility and Child step out. Herald walks up to Ratchet 
Herald: "hello, we are the keepers, we are allied with you Maximals, we have 
things that might help in re-creating the arc, These ships were made at about 
the same time as the Ark. Use them at your will."

Tranquility yells out to The Maximals Gathered around the Ark: "Who is in 
charge here?!"
